id-users-tweet-limit-to-10000-characters-041452623.html">提高</a>到 25,000 个字符，甚至正在<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-is-working-on-new-publishing-tools-for-long-form-articles-185302573.html">开发新工具</a>来发布长格式内容。该网站还将视频时长限制扩大到 3 小时。与此同时，社交网络对免费用户的吸引力越来越小。该公司在 7 月份宣布，将限制非付费用户可以发送的 DM 数量，以限制垃圾邮件，并且由于“极端水平的数据抓取”，该公司此前还对用户每天可以看到的推文数量<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-puts-strict-cap-on-how-many-tweets-users-can-read-each-day-182623928.html">设置了严格的上限。</a> ”。虽然这一限制是暂时的，但未经验证的账户最初每天只能发帖 600 个。</p><p>应用程序开发人员 Alessandro Paluzzi 在三月份首次<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-may-let-you-hide-the-fact-you-pay-to-use-twitter-160015039.html">发现了</a>隐藏复选标记的功能。根据帕鲁兹分享的屏幕截图，验证过程将保持不变，用户需要提交政府身份证件来验证其身份。现在，乍一看并不会明显看出有人在为 X Blue 付费。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/x-blue-subscribers-can-now-hide-their-checkmarks-110229094.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/x-blue-subscribers-can-now-hide-their-checkmarks-110229094.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> eee28387-bc72-4ff4-b271-88d362d1936e</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 02 Aug 2023 11:02:29 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690977918</ingested><modified> 2023-08-02T12:05:21+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="2445" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/9402bbc0-3117-11ee-a67f-dd0246e993ed" width="3668"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><m